0:{"buildId":"I3GEKSVLVTWqxcEXDRaWq","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"ISO 10002 Complaint Handling"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:30:33+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"ISO 10002 Complaint handling in Abu Dhabi is essential for companies increases the productivity of the organization to achieve ISO 10002 Certification at low"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 10002 Complaint Handling"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"WIZMS ISO consultant in Dubai provides first-rate ISO consulting services such as ISO Consulting, ISO Certification, and ISO Training in UAE, Gap analysis, Documentation, Implementation, and ISO certification audits in UAE."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Organizations pursue quality in a variety of ways. In truth, there are many areas of business that firms may be proud of, like ISO standards, dependable goods, excellent services, and environmentally friendly methods, to mention a few. However, no matter how much careful work is put toward a wide range of quality measures, at the end of the day, customer happiness is the most important factor for many firms.WIZMS focuses on raising awareness, providing ISO training, and implementing Complaints Handling Standards to save time and money for the industry. WIZMS, ISO consultant in Dubai follows the listed methodology for obtaining ISO 10002 in Dubai for your firm."}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 10002:2015 certification in Dubai provides rules for the complaint handling procedure. This process is connected to an organization's goods and services and includes planning, design, development, operation, maintenance, and improvement. The complaints-handling procedure is appropriate for inclusion as one of the procedures of a complete quality management system. The ISO 10002 standard helps in identifying complaints, their causes, and how to effectively and efficiently resolve complaints.Many of these ideas will be recognizable to anyone who has used other quality management standards, notably ISO 9001. Because the complaint-handling procedure outlined in ISO 10002:2015. It is appropriate for use as one of the procedures of a broader quality management system."}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 10002 checklists:"}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Create a customer-focused atmosphere through soliciting feedback, addressing any complaints, boosting the organization's capacity to develop its goods and services, and increasing customer service. As a result of ISO 10002:2015, customer satisfaction has increased."}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Our ISO consultants in Dubai will include senior management in the process and make the essential commitments through proper resource acquisition and deployment, including people training."}],"$L2","$L3","$L4","$L5","$L6","$L7","$L8","$L9","$La","$Lb","$Lc","$Ld","$Le"]}],"$Lf"]}]}],["$L10"],"$L11"]}],"loading":null,"isPartial":false}
2:["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Recognizing and responding to ISO 10002 complainants' requirements and expectations;"}]
3:["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Provides a complaint procedure that is transparent, effective, and simple to use;"}]
4:["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Analyzing and analyzing complaints to improve product and service quality, particularly customer service;"}]
5:["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The complaint-handling procedure is being audited following ISO 10002 standards."}]
6:["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Examining the efficacy and efficiency of the complaint-handling procedure."}]
7:["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Guidelines for ISO 10002 certification for Organizations"}]
8:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The ISO 10002 Standard provides guidelines for establishing, implementing, maintaining, and enhancing customer satisfaction policies and procedures."}]
9:["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"This ISO 10002 checklist applies to product and service-related codes that contain promises made to consumers about an organization's behavior. These promises and related provisions are intended to increase customer satisfaction."}]
a:["$","p","15",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 10002 certification is aimed for use by any business, regardless of its type or size, or the products and services it provides, including businesses that create customer satisfaction standards of conduct for other firms to employ."}]
b:["$","p","16",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"This ISO 10002 standard is intended for customer satisfaction codes of conduct involving individual customers purchasing or utilizing products, property, or services for personal or home reasons, although it applies to all customer satisfaction codes of conduct."}]
c:["$","p","17",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"This certification does not specify the substantive substance of customer satisfaction codes of conduct, nor does it cover other sorts of codes of conduct, such as those relating to an organization's engagement with its workers or with its suppliers."}]
d:["$","p","18",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"We are a leading independent certification provider to a variety of industries in the UAE and Dubai. Our goal is to enable organizations to categorize and minimize risk in operations and business processes. You can simply contact WIZMS by going to www.wizms.net and chatting with an expert, or you can send an email to mahendran@wizms.net and an expert will contact you as soon as possible to give the best solution available in the market. Working with WIZMS for ISO 10002 certification provides further confidence that the company can handle effective road safety management systems. A Complaint Management System that is supported by industry standards such as ISO 10002 certification in Dubai will assure high levels of customer satisfaction and that your firm is client-centric."}]
e:["$","p","19",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO Certification in UAE is the most recognized Certification Standard among UAE small and medium businesses. WIZMS offers ISO Certificate in UAE for all key standards, including ISO 9001:2015, ISO 14001:2015, ISO 27001:2015, ISO 17025:2015, ISO 45001:2015, and others. WIZMS is the leading ISO consultant in the UAE, offering ISO consulting services in Dubai,Abu Dhabi, Sharjah, Ras al-Khaimah, Ajman, Al Ain, and Fujairah."}]
f:["$","footer",null,{"className":"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"ISO 10002 Complaint Handling in Abu Dhabi"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"ISO 10002 Certification."}]]}]}]
